   "source": [
    "## 4. DuckDB-analyse — SQL mot GeoDataFrame\n",
    "\n",
    "Vi bruker DuckDB sin spatial-extension for å køyre SQL-spørjingar direkte mot GeoPandas-DataFramen.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "745b86bb",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-04-21T10:05:31.456761Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-04-21T10:05:31.456522Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-04-21T10:05:31.995738Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-04-21T10:05:31.994566Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "(DuckDB spatial-extension ikkje tilgjengeleg: IOException) — held fram med rein SQL\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<div>\n",
       "<style scoped>\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n",
